2 Biparietal diameter (BPD)

# data preparation convert to long format
blood_child_weight_long <- fetal_growth %>%
    pivot_longer(cols = starts_with("BPD_"), names_to = "BPD_time", names_prefix = "BPD_",
        values_to = "BPD_value", values_drop_na = FALSE)


blood_child_weight_long$BPD_time <- factor(blood_child_weight_long$BPD_time, levels = c("pgv2",
    "pgv3", "pgv4", "pgv5"))

## assign visit variable
blood_child_weight_long_visit <- blood_child_weight_long %>%
    group_by(Subject_ID) %>%
    arrange(BPD_time) %>%
    dplyr::mutate(visit = 1:n()) %>%
    arrange(Subject_ID)
blood_weight_plot1 <- blood_child_weight_long_visit %>%
    ggplot(aes(x = BPD_value, fill = BPD_time)) + geom_histogram() + facet_grid2(cols = vars(BPD_time),
    scale = "free", independent = "all")


blood_weight_plot1

blood_weight_plot2 <- blood_child_weight_long_visit %>%
    ggplot(aes(y = BPD_value, x = BPD_time, fill = BPD_time)) + geom_boxplot()


blood_weight_plot2

6 Estimated fetal weight (in gm)

Formula: Log10 weight = 1.3596 - 0.00386(AC x FL) + 0.0064 HC + 0.00061(BPD x AC) + 0.0424 AC + 0.174 FL note: Fetal measurements in cm; fetal weight in gm.

fetal_growth <- fetal_growth %>%
    mutate(BPD_pgv2 = BPD_pgv2/10, BPD_pgv3 = BPD_pgv3/10, BPD_pgv4 = BPD_pgv4/10,
        BPD_pgv5 = BPD_pgv5/10, HC_pgv2 = HC_pgv2/10, HC_pgv3 = HC_pgv3/10, HC_pgv4 = HC_pgv4/10,
        HC_pgv5 = HC_pgv5/10, AC_pgv2 = AC_pgv2/10, AC_pgv3 = AC_pgv3/10, AC_pgv4 = AC_pgv4/10,
        AC_pgv5 = AC_pgv5/10, FL_pgv2 = FL_pgv2/10, FL_pgv3 = FL_pgv3/10, FL_pgv4 = FL_pgv4/10,
        FL_pgv5 = FL_pgv5/10, EFW_pgv2 = 10^(1.3596 - 0.00386 * (AC_pgv2 * FL_pgv2) +
            0.0064 * HC_pgv2 + 0.00061 * (BPD_pgv2 * AC_pgv2) + 0.0424 * AC_pgv2 +
            0.174 * FL_pgv2), EFW_pgv3 = 10^(1.3596 - 0.00386 * (AC_pgv3 * FL_pgv3) +
            0.0064 * HC_pgv3 + 0.00061 * (BPD_pgv3 * AC_pgv3) + 0.0424 * AC_pgv3 +
            0.174 * FL_pgv3), EFW_pgv4 = 10^(1.3596 - 0.00386 * (AC_pgv4 * FL_pgv4) +
            0.0064 * HC_pgv4 + 0.00061 * (BPD_pgv4 * AC_pgv4) + 0.0424 * AC_pgv4 +
            0.174 * FL_pgv4), EFW_pgv5 = 10^(1.3596 - 0.00386 * (AC_pgv5 * FL_pgv5) +
            0.0064 * HC_pgv5 + 0.00061 * (BPD_pgv5 * AC_pgv5) + 0.0424 * AC_pgv5 +
            0.174 * FL_pgv5))
